18:24.603 --> 18:29.308 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICOLE RASMUSON, iPrep Academy:
We all started
at the very beginning, and then
some just

18:29.342 --> 18:30.810 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
